snippet.title: Dordogne - Official Release Window Trailer | The MIX Showcase March 2023
snippet.description:
Dordogne will be available on Nintendo Switch, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and PC in spring 2023. Watch the latest trailer for another look at Dordogne's beautiful world and learn a bit more about the story of this upcoming narrative game. 

In Dordogne, play as Mimi, exploring the precious recollections of your childhood and the times shared with your late grandmother. As past meets present, confront your adult choices with fond childhood memories to uncover lost family secrets.
